<p>Torta clones filelights&apos;s way to represent disk usage.
usage example:</p>

<p>(torta:torta &ldquo;/home/pepito&rdquo; :output &ldquo;output.swf&rdquo;)</p>

<p>special note: if you are keeping separated source and binary files, be sure that the freeserif.fo file is at the right directory when you load torta</p>
